
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant GQ as graph-query
    participant GI as graph-ingest
    participant GX as graph-index

    C->>GQ: NATS Request: graph.query.pathSearch
    GQ->>GI: graph.ingest.query.entity
    GI->>GQ: Entity data
    GQ->>GX: graph.index.query.outgoing
    GX->>GQ: Relationships
    GQ->>GQ: PathSearcher traversal logic
    GQ->>C: NATS Reply: path results

